<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-11267] Trait static methods are not resolved when called from closure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-11267</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In trait when calling a method from closure. MissingMethodException thrown inside that method when calling any other trait static method. (This is not the case when &lt;b&gt;class&lt;/b&gt; is used instead of &lt;b&gt;trait&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When in &quot;ugly&quot; case, &lt;em&gt;&lt;b&gt;this&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/em&gt; context is switched to &lt;em&gt;&lt;b&gt;TestTrait$Trait$Helper&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/em&gt; from &lt;em&gt;&lt;b&gt;TestClass&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Test code&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
TestClass.getLevel1() &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// run test
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;TestClass &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; TestTrait{}

trait TestTrait{
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; getLevel1(){  println([&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;getLevel1&apos;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;])
        getLevel2(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;good&apos;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// runs
&lt;/span&gt;        def me = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bad&apos;&lt;/span&gt;.with{me.getLevel2(it)} &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// runs
&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ugly&apos;&lt;/span&gt;.with{getLevel2(it)} &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; getLevel3 not found
&lt;/span&gt;    }
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; getLevel2(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; s){  println([&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;getLevel2&apos;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;])
        getLevel3(s) &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; MissingMethodException &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; ugly
&lt;/span&gt;    }
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; getLevel3(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; s){  println([&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;getLevel3&apos;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;])
        s
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-none&quot;&gt;
No signature of method: static TestTrait.getLevel3() is applicable for argument types: (String) values: [ugly]&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
